%20on%20direct-to-consumer%20shipments%20of%20less%20than%20%24800.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20House%20Select%20Committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fselectcommitteeontheccp.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fselect-committee-releases-interim-findings-shein-temu-forced-labor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20last%20year%20estimated%20that%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20packages%20shipped%20to%20the%20US%20under%20the%20de%20minimis%20provision%20came%20from%20Shein%20and%20Temu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration's%20announcement%20included%20a%20new%20rule%20proposal%20that%20would%20remove%20this%20exemption%20for%20many%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F09%2F13%2Fnx-s1-5111427%2Fshein-temu-white-house-biden-rule-china%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%3C%2Fa%3E%20clothing%20products.%20These%20imports%20would%20become%20subject%20to%20import%20taxes%20and%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20leading%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20the%20many%20Americans%20who%20buy%20apparel%2C%20home%20decor%2C%20or%20electronics%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Shein%20and%20Temu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Shein%20and%20Temu's%20costs%20rise%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethis%20could%20hit%20Gen%20Z%20the%20hardest.%20An%20estimated%2040%25%20to%2045%25%20of%20Shein%20and%20Temu's%20US%20customers%20are%20Gen%20Z%2C%20Chad%20Schofield%2C%20cofounder%20of%20the%20e-commerce%20logistics%20management%20platform%20BoxC%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20the%20proposal%20sparked%20some%20backlash%20among%20young%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNineteen-year-old%20girls%20will%20scream%20bloody%20murder%20if%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20proposal%20goes%20into%20effect%2C%20a%20%2440%20Shein%20or%20Temu%20purchase%2C%20for%20example%2C%20could%20become%20roughly%20%2450%20once%20the%20new%20import%20fees%20are%20added%20%E2%80%94%20effectively%20a%2025%25%20increase%20%E2%80%94%20Schofield%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHowever%2C%20import%20fees%20could%20vary%20by%20product.%20Juozas%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20e-commerce%20intelligence%20firm%20Marketplace%20Pulse%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20many%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20products%20would%20likely%20face%20import%20fees%20between%2015%25%20and%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20aims%20to%20help%20protect%20American%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20from%20a%20rapidly%20growing%20number%20of%20imports.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20number%20of%20annual%20de%20minimis%20shipments%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F09%2F13%2Ffact-sheet-biden-harris-administration-announces-new-actions-to-protect-american-consumers-workers-and-businesses-by-cracking-down-on-de-minimis-shipments-with-unsafe-unfairly-traded-products%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrown%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20roughly%20140%20million%20to%20one%20billion%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F14%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Ftariffs-amazon-walmart-china-shein.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20these%20shipments%20come%20from%20China%20than%20all%20other%20countries%20combined.%20In%20a%20fact%20sheet%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20said%20the%20rise%20in%20these%20shipments%20has%20made%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20the%20US%20to%20enforce%20trade%20laws%2C%20protect%20consumers%2C%20and%20prevent%20illicit%20drugs%20like%20fentanyl%20from%20entering%20the%20country%20because%20these%20shipments%20face%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F09%2F13%2Fnx-s1-5111427%2Fshein-temu-white-house-biden-rule-china%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20lax%3C%2Fa%3E%20customs%20inspections.%20There%20is%20also%20concern%20that%20competition%20from%20these%20low-cost%20imports%20is%20hurting%20US%20businesses%20that%20can't%20compete%20on%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20administration%20didn't%20name%20Shein%20or%20Temu%20directly%20in%20its%20announcement%2C%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20these%20companies%20were%20likely%20top%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epart%20of%20a%20broader%20Biden%20administration%20effort%20to%20protect%20US%20businesses%20from%20competition%20with%20cheap%20Chinese%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ensure%20the%20US%20isn't%20reliant%20on%20China%2C%20in%20part%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-proposes-ban-china-russia-tech-connected-cars-security-fears-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20security%20reasons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20same%20day%20the%20administration%20announced%20its%20rule%20proposal%2C%20new%20tariffs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail-consumer%2Fus-take-steps-curb-low-value-chinese-shipments-under-800-de-minimis-exemption-2024-09-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etook%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20target%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-solar-tariffs-china-shock-economy-property-trade-war-krugman-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2418%20billion%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20including%20solar%20cells%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%20Meanwhile%2C%20challenges%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-app-american-us-not-worried-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanning%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20are%20heading%20to%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20many%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Xers%20are%20also%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fmillennials-gen-xers-not-gen-143000810.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20many%20Americans%20across%20generations%20aren't%20fans%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-vs-shein-fast-fashion-rivals-legal-battle-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20companies%20specialize%20in%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-and-temu-skirt-import-tariffs-us-lawmakers-fast-fashion-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20product%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-shoes-11-229-times-legal-limit-toxic-substances-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafety%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228458a751-d271-4d33-ad54-7d35c9ec98e7%5C%22%3EHow%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20could%20work%20around%20the%20proposal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20prices%20rise%20on%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20goods%2C%20it%20could%20help%20some%20companies%20that%20don't%20source%20as%20many%20of%20their%20products%20from%20China.%20This%20includes%20large%20e-commerce%20businesses%20like%20Amazon.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20on%20Temu%20is%20also%20on%20Amazon%20but%20more%20expensive%20and%20faster%20shipping%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20price%20gap%20between%20the%20same%20product%20on%20Amazon%20and%20Temu%20is%20going%20to%20shrink%20but%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20disappear%20completely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eremains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20much%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20%E2%80%94%20prices%20will%20rise%20for%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchofield%20estimated%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20proposal%20wouldn't%20take%20effect%20for%20at%20least%2018%20months%2C%20at%20which%20point%20another%20president%20will%20be%20in%20office.%20He%20said%20a%20public%20comment%20period%20is%20required%20and%20that%20the%20e-commerce%20industry%20could%20lobby%20against%20it.%20If%20Congress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-de-minimis-tax-loophole-scrutiny-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassed%20a%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20revised%20the%20de%20minimis%20provision%20%E2%80%94%20something%20the%20administration%20has%20pushed%20for%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rollout%20of%20import%20fees%20could%20be%20expedited%20and%20potentially%20hit%20consumers%20sooner%20than%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20re-elected%2C%20he%20could%20also%20decide%20to%20change%20course%2C%20though%20Schofield%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20expect%20him%20to%20given%20his%20prior%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-does-trump-vance-stand-on-china-tariffs-inflation-taxes-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolicy%20stances%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20China.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20wins%2C%20she%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20pursue%20a%20similar%20course%20as%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20once%20these%20fees%20took%20effect%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20ways%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20could%20try%20to%20keep%20prices%20low%20for%20consumers.%20For%20one%2C%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20could%20%26quot%3Bshare%20the%20burden%26quot%3B%20with%20customers%2C%20raising%20prices%20modestly%20but%20subsidizing%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20import%20fees%2C%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20could%20reduce%20their%20direct-to-consumer%20shipments%20from%20China%20and%20bring%20more%20of%20their%20inventory%20to%20warehouses%20in%20the%20US%20for%20distribution.%20Schofield%20said%20these%20companies%20are%20already%20warehousing%20some%20of%20their%20more%20popular%20products%20and%20that%20leaning%20into%20this%20further%20could%20help%20them%20keep%20costs%20low%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20de%20minimis%20reforms%20come%20to%20pass%2C%20Schofield%20said%20Temu%20or%20Shein%20could%20avoid%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20the%20new%20import%20fees%20by%20importing%20large%20product%20shipments%20to%20store%20at%20US%20warehouses.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20would%20pay%20fees%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bmanufacturing%20cost%26quot%3B%20in%20China%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20retail%20price%20a%20US%20consumer%20would%20face%20for%20a%20direct-to-consumer%20purchase%20from%20China.%20Schofield%20said%20the%20manufacturing%20cost%20could%20often%20be%20roughly%20half%20of%20the%20retail%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20warehousing%20strategy%20would%20still%20force%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20to%20pay%20import%20fees%20that%20they%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20when%20it%20was%20shipping%20sub-%24800%20orders%20directly%20to%20consumers%20from%20China.%20The%20companies%20could%20choose%20to%20increase%20prices%20as%20a%20result%2C%20but%20Schofield%20said%20he'd%20expect%20the%20increases%20to%20be%20considerably%20lower%20than%20what%20a%20consumer%20would%20encounter%20with%20a%20direct%20shipment%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20Chinese%20companies%20like%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20could%20seek%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F14%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Ftariffs-amazon-walmart-china-shein.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimport%3C%2Fa%3E%20goods%20from%20Canada%20or%20Mexico%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20them%20to%20bypass%20the%20import%20fees%20that%20de%20minimis%20reforms%20would%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20strategic%20shifts%20would%20require%20the%20companies%20to%20stray%20from%20the%20direct-to-consumer%20models%20that%20have%20fueled%20their%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292b214fa-8361-4e48-8e4b-d4c6d2e9018b%5C%22%3EThe%20proposals%20would%20affect%20more%20than%20just%20Shein%20and%20Temu%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20that%20could%20raise%20prices%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20proposal.%20Schofield%20said%20many%20US%20businesses%20also%20import%20goods%20direct-to-consumer%20from%20Chinese%20factories.%20This%20includes%20smaller%20businesses%20and%20startups%20that%20don't%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20warehouse%20their%20goods%20in%20the%20US.%20They%20would%20face%20these%20import%20fees%20as%20well%2C%20and%20Schofield%20said%20they'd%20likely%20have%20a%20tougher%20time%20adapting%20than%20companies%20the%20size%20of%20Shein%20or%20Temu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20affects%20anything%20that's%20being%20shipped%20direct-to-consumer%20from%20China%20%E2%80%94%20any%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20purely%20Temu%20or%20Shein%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20proposal%20was%20announced%2C%20both%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20have%20said%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%20is%20not%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ekey%20to%20their%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%2C%20a%20Temu%20spokesperson%20pointed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-de-minimis-tax-loophole-scrutiny-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomments%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20made%20in%20February.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20Temu's%20%26quot%3Bsupply-chain%20efficiencies%20and%20operational%20proficiencies%26quot%3B%20were%20the%20primary%20drivers%20of%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20open%20to%20and%20supportive%20of%20any%20policy%20adjustments%20made%20by%20legislators%20that%20align%20with%20consumer%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20as%20long%20as%20these%20policies%20are%20fair%2C%20they%20won't%20influence%20the%20outcomes%20of%20competitive%20business%20dynamics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Shein%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20that%20complying%20with%20any%20reforms%20to%20US%20trade%20law%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btop%20priority%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20success%20is%20anchored%20in%20our%20unique%20on-demand%20business%20model%2C%20which%20allows%20us%20to%20bring%20customers%20the%20styles%20they%20want%2C%20efficiently%20and%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShein%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20neither%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%20nor%20Schofield%20said%20they%20expect%20the%20import%20fees%20to%20take%20much%20wind%20out%20of%20Shein%20or%20Temu's%20sails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTemu%20and%20Shein%20won't%20disappear%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20disruptive%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20price%20is%20the%20ultimate%20value%20proposition%20then%20they'll%20continue%20to%20steal%20market%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchofield%20said%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20have%20already%20been%20paying%20similar%20import%20fees%20for%20years%20in%20Canada%2C%20and%20they%20still%20have%20a%20large%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20that%20work%20in%20Canada%2C%20they%20could%20adapt%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20them%20really%20slowing%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20save%20money%20by%20buying%20from%20Shein%20and%20Temu%3F%20Are%20you%20willing%20to%20share%20your%20story%3F%20If%20so%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20