it%20a%20flat%20pitch.%20The%20pitch%20curator%20and%20Gillespie%20want%20to%20play%20on%20the%20same%20pitch.%20I%20would%20be%20really%20happy%20if%20the%20match%20took%20place%20on%20a%20grassy%20surface%20and%20our%20bowlers%20took%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20previous%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20in%202022%2C%20England%20swept%20aside%20Pakistan%203-0%20in%20a%20ruthless%20manner%20with%20their%20%26quot%3BBazball%26quot%3B%20approach%20producing%20rich%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20veteran%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%20hoped%20the%20team's%20series%20win%20against%20Pakistan%20two%20years%20ago%20would%20help%20the%20visitors%20formulate%20their%20plans%2C%20but%20emphasised%20that%20the%20visitors%20will%20have%20to%20be%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20that%20series%20has%20helped%20us%20prepare%20for%20the%20coming%20matches%20and%20we%20have%20a%20plan%20on%20how%20to%20play%20here.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20new%20series%20and%20we%20have%20to%20play%20well%20again%20to%20win%20again%20in%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20Root%20told%20a%20media%20conference%20here%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20learned%20a%20few%20things%20from%20that%20series%2C%20but%20(playing%20against)%20Pakistan%20at%20home%20is%20a%20challenge.%20Pakistan%20can%20definitely%20take%20advantage%20of%20their%20home%20conditions%20and%20we%20also%20have%20a%20couple%20of%20new%20young%20players%20eager%20to%20establish%20themselves.%20It%20should%20be%20an%20interesting%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728192000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F46jn1u5g_jason-gillespie-afp_625x300_06_Octobe