hip%20or%20mid-level%20roles%20working%20on%20specified%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323501%2Figniting-ideas-for-impact-audiobook-explores-pioneering-indian-startups%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20work%20with%20developers%20or%20people%20in%20leadership%20roles%20with%20anywhere%20between%20three%20to%2012%20years%20of%20experience.%20We%20do%20have%20plans%20in%20the%20future%20to%20help%20women%20in%20other%20industries%2C%20but%20today%2C%20our%20vision%20is%20to%20try%20and%20solve%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20main%20focus%20is%20not%20just%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20talent.%20We%20also%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20companies%20who%20are%20going%20to%20hire%20them.%20Companies%20also%20have%20to%20trust%20women%20to%20give%20them%20a%20chance.%20Our%20focus%20lies%20in%20balancing%20their%20respective%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20focused%20on%20seamlessly%20reintegrating%20women%20with%20three%20or%20more%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20back%20into%20the%20workforce%20after%20they%20had%20to%20leave%20it%20for%20reasons%20like%20marriage%2C%20relocation%2C%20childbirth%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20start%20with%20women%20with%20three%20years%20of%20experience%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20our%20statistical%20findings%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20after%20three%20years%20in%20the%20workforce%20when%20women%20get%20married%20and%20relocate%20to%20where%20their%20husbands%20work.%20Once%20they%20c