l%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20the%20Mayurbhanj%20district%20of%20Odisha.%20Found%20unattended%20by%20people%20of%20the%20Kharia%20tribal%20community%2C%20Saroj%20would%20name%20her%20%E2%80%98Khairi%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20seven%20years%2C%20Khairi%20would%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98free-living%20family%20member%E2%80%99%20at%20Choudhury%E2%80%99s%20official%20bungalow%20in%20Jashipur.%20She%20was%20fed%20with%20mutton%20and%20milk%20powder%2C%20slept%20on%20their%20beds%20and%20often%20played%20with%20them.%20Saroj%20closely%20observed%20her%20to%20study%20the%20various%20behavioural%20aspects%20of%20tigers%2C%20especially%20the%20use%20of%20pheromones%2C%20their%20mating%20behaviour%20and%20territoriality%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20long%20before%20Saroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20took%20over%20as%20the%20Simlipal%20Tiger%20Reserve%E2%80%99s%20first%20Field%20Director%20and%20met%20Khairi%2C%20he%20had%20already%20established%20himself%20as%20a%20pioneer%20of%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20particularly%20of%20tigers%2C%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20developing%20the%20pugmark%20tracking%20technique%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20bedrock%20of%20organising%20tiger%20censuses%20in%20India%20till%202004%20and%20the%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20much%20vaunted%20Project%20Tiger%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20to%20mentoring%20generations%20of%20forest%20officers%20in%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20Choudhury%20remains%20a%20legendary%20conservationist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F17145020%2FSaroj-Raj-Choudury-12.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20with%20Khairi%20%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-233089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20with%20